<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b17Nov1932"><font color="red">17 November 1932</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to F.V. Morely): I have had two applications from the Servire Press editors of Transition asking for the right to publish in a deluxe edition of the new fragment of Work in Progress. </div>
